            <article class="relative rounded-2xl border-t-4 border-brandAmber bg-white p-8 shadow-card">
              <span class="absolute right-8 top-4 rounded-full bg-brandAmber px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-white">MOST POPULAR</span>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primaryText">Pro</h3>
              <p class="mt-4 text-4xl font-extrabold text-primaryText">₹299 <span class="text-base font-medium text-secondaryText">/month</span></p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-gray-400 line-through">Compare: eZee ₹5,000 - DJUBO ₹2,000</p>
              <ul class="mt-6 space-y-2 text-primaryText">
                <li><span class="text-successGreen">✓</span> Everything in Free</li>
                <li><span class="text-successGreen">✓</span> Unlimited rooms</li>
                <li><span class="text-successGreen">✓</span> Unlimited calendar syncs</li>
                <li><span class="text-successGreen">✓</span> WhatsApp daily summary</li>
