          <p class="mx-auto mt-8 max-w-3xl text-center text-base italic text-secondaryText">
            ₹299/month. That's less than one night in your cheapest room. And you're losing ₹15,000/month without it.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="faq" class="fade-section px-5 py-16 md:px-8 md:py-24">
        <div class="site-wrap mx-auto">
          <p class="section-label text-xs font-bold">FAQ</p>
          <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold text-primaryText md:text-4xl">Common questions</h2>

          <div class="mt-10 space-y-4" id="faq-list">
            <article class="faq-item rounded-xl border border-black/10 p-5">
              <button class="faq-toggle flex w-full items-center justify-between gap-4 text-left">
                <span class="font-semibold text-primaryText">How is StayDocs different from eZee or DJUBO?</span>
                <span class="faq-arrow text-brandAmber">⌄</span>
              </button>
              <div class="faq-content pt-0">
                <p class="pt-3 text-secondaryText">They're full hotel systems for 50-room properties. ₹2,000-15,000/month. Hours to learn. StayDocs is a simple booking dashboard for 1-15 room properties. ₹299/month. 5 minutes to set up.</p>
              </div>
            </article>

            <article class="faq-item rounded-xl border border-black/10 p-5">
              <button class="faq-toggle flex w-full items-center justify-between gap-4 text-left">
                <span class="font-semibold text-primaryText">Will it work with my Airbnb and Booking.com?</span>
                <span class="faq-arrow text-brandAmber">⌄</span>
              </button>
              <div class="faq-content"><p class="pt-3 text-secondaryText">Yes. Paste your calendar export link and bookings sync automatically every 15 minutes.</p></div>
            </article>

            <article class="faq-item rounded-xl border border-black/10 p-5">
              <button class="faq-toggle flex w-full items-center justify-between gap-4 text-left">
                <span class="font-semibold text-primaryText">Can my receptionist use it?</span>
                <span class="faq-arrow text-brandAmber">⌄</span>
              </button>
              <div class="faq-content"><p class="pt-3 text-secondaryText">If they can use WhatsApp, they can use StayDocs. And with the daily WhatsApp summary, they don't even need to open the app.</p></div>
            </article>

            <article class="faq-item rounded-xl border border-black/10 p-5">
              <button class="faq-toggle flex w-full items-center justify-between gap-4 text-left">
                <span class="font-semibold text-primaryText">What if I only have 3-5 rooms?</span>
                <span class="faq-arrow text-brandAmber">⌄</span>
              </button>
              <div class="faq-content"><p class="pt-3 text-secondaryText">Perfect. That's exactly who we built this for. The free plan supports 3 rooms.</p></div>
            </article>

            <article class="faq-item rounded-xl border border-black/10 p-5">
              <button class="faq-toggle flex w-full items-center justify-between gap-4 text-left">
                <span class="font-semibold text-primaryText">Is my data safe?</span>
                <span class="faq-arrow text-brandAmber">⌄</span>
              </button>
              <div class="faq-content"><p class="pt-3 text-secondaryText">Enterprise-grade encryption. You can delete your account and all data anytime.</p></div>
            </article>

            <article class="faq-item rounded-xl border border-black/10 p-5">
              <button class="faq-toggle flex w-full items-center justify-between gap-4 text-left">
                <span class="font-semibold text-primaryText">Does it work offline?</span>
                <span class="faq-arrow text-brandAmber">⌄</span>
              </button>
              <div class="faq-content"><p class="pt-3 text-secondaryText">It caches your recent data so you can view your dashboard even with a weak connection.</p></div>
            </article>

            <article class="faq-item rounded-xl border border-black/10 p-5">
              <button class="faq-toggle flex w-full items-center justify-between gap-4 text-left">
                <span class="font-semibold text-primaryText">What happens after I join the waitlist?</span>
                <span class="faq-arrow text-brandAmber">⌄</span>
              </button>
              <div class="faq-content"><p class="pt-3 text-secondaryText">You'll get notified when we launch. Early members get extended free trial and priority support.</p></div>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="final-cta" class="fade-section bg-brandCharcoal px-5 py-16 md:px-8 md:py-24">
        <div class="site-wrap mx-auto text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto inline-flex rounded-2xl bg-white p-3 shadow-card">
            <img src="assets/staydocs-logo-cropped.png" alt="StayDocs brand logo" class="h-16 w-auto" />
          </div>

          <h2 class="mt-7 text-3xl font-extrabold text-white md:text-4xl">Ready to simplify your bookings?</h2>
          <p class="mx-auto mt-3 max-w-2xl text-base text-[#B0B0B0]">Join 200+ property owners. We'll notify you when StayDocs launches.</p>

          <form class="mx-auto mt-9 grid max-w-5xl gap-3 md:grid-cols-5" action="#" method="post" novalidate>
            <input class="h-12 rounded-lg border border-white/15 bg-[#3D3D3D] px-4 text-white placeholder:text-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brandAmber" type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your Name" />
            <input class="h-12 rounded-lg border border-white/15 bg-[#3D3D3D] px-4 text-white placeholder:text-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brandAmber" type="tel" name="phone" placeholder="Phone (+91)" />
            <input class="h-12 rounded-lg border border-white/15 bg-[#3D3D3D] px-4 text-white placeholder:text-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brandAmber" type="text" name="property" placeholder="Property Name" />
            <input class="h-12 rounded-lg border border-white/15 bg-[#3D3D3D] px-4 text-white placeholder:text-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brandAmber" type="text" name="city" placeholder="City" />
            <button class="h-12 rounded-lg bg-brandAmber px-5 font-semibold text-white" type="submit">Join Waitlist -></button>
          </form>

          <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-gray-400">No credit card - No spam - Free to join</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-footerDark px-5 py-12 md:px-8">
      <div class="site-wrap mx-auto grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div>
          <img src="assets/staydocs-logo-cropped.png" alt="StayDocs logo" class="h-16 w-auto rounded bg-white p-2" />
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-secondaryText">All Your Bookings In One Place</p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-start gap-4 text-sm text-white">
          <a href="#features" class="hover:text-brandAmber">Features</a>
          <a href="#pricing" class="hover:text-brandAmber">Pricing</a>
          <a href="#faq" class="hover:text-brandAmber">FAQ</a>
          <a href="#" class="hover:text-brandAmber">Privacy Policy</a>
          <a href="#" class="hover:text-brandAmber">Terms of Service</a>
        </div>

        <div class="text-sm text-white">
          <p>WhatsApp us: +91 XXXXXXXXXX</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="site-wrap mx-auto mt-8 border-t border-white/10 pt-5 text-sm text-secondaryText">
        © 2026 StayDocs - Built in India 🇮🇳
      </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
      const nav = document.getElementById('navbar');
      const mobileMenu = document.getElementById('mobile-menu');
      const menuBtn = document.getElementById('menu-btn');

      menuBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
        mobileMenu.classList.toggle('hidden');
      });

      window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
        if (window.scrollY > 12) {
          nav.classList.add('shadow-nav');
        } else {
          nav.classList.remove('shadow-nav');
        }
      });

      document.querySelectorAll('#mobile-menu a').forEach((link) => {
        link.addEventListener('click', () => mobileMenu.classList.add('hidden'));
      });

      const observer = new IntersectionObserver(
        (entries) => {
          entries.forEach((entry) => {
            if (entry.isIntersecting) {
              entry.target.classList.add('in-view');
            }
          });
        },
        { threshold: 0.15 }
      );

      document.querySelectorAll('.fade-section').forEach((section) => observer.observe(section));

      const faqItems = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item');
      faqItems.forEach((item) => {
        const btn = item.querySelector('.faq-toggle');
        btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
          faqItems.forEach((other) => {
            if (other !== item) other.classList.remove('open');
          });
          item.classList.toggle('open');
        });
      });
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
